<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609648>
    dc:description "FIGURES 169–182. Trichobothrial setae on pedicel: 169—Sirthenea africana Distant, 1903; 170—S. flaviceps (Signoret, 1860); 171—S. picescens Reuter, 1887; 172—S. rodhaini Schouteden, 1913; 173—S. caiana Chłond, 2008; 174—S. dimidiata Horváth, 1911; 175—S. flavipes (Stål, 1855); 176—S. kali sp. nov.; 177—S. nigronitens (Miller, 1958); 178—S. nitida Chłond, 2008; 179—S. nigra Cai & Tomokuni, 2004; 180—S. setosa sp. nov.; 181—S. laevicollis Horváth, 1909; 182—S. obscura (Stål, 1866)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609652>
    dc:description "FIGURES 188–192. 188—Ridges of metapleura of Sirthenea caiana Chłond, 2008; 189—U-shape posterior margin of an eye of S. obscura (Stål, 1866); 190—S-shape posterior margin of an eye of S. flaviceps (Signoret, 1860); 191—Ridges of proepisternum and proepimeron of S. africana Distant, 1903; 192—Ridges of proepisternum and proepimeron of S. nigronitens (Miller, 1958)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609652/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609660>
    dc:description "FIGURES 205–208. Color figures of habitus: 205—Sirthenea nitida Chłond, 2008; 206—S. nigra Cai & Tomokuni, 2004; 207—S. setosa sp. nov.; 208—S. obscura (Stål, 1866)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609660/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609635>
    dc:description "FIGURE 144. Sirthenea obscura (Stål, 1866)—dorsal habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2609637>
    dc:description "FIGURES 145–152. Sirthenea obscura (Stål, 1866): 145—pygophore, dorsal view; 146—left paramere, inner view; 147—left paramere, outer view; 148—right paramere, lateral view; 149—right paramere, outer view; 150—phallus, right lateral view; 151—phallus, left lateral view; 152—phallus, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2609637/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

